Lustre Client: CentOS 6.5/x86_64 (kernel version: 2.6.32-431.1.2.0.1.el6.x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
Lustre Server: CentOS 6.4/x86_64 (kernel version: 2.6.32-358.23.2.el6_lustre.x86_64)&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
